{% doc %}
  @prompt
    请使用 HTML 和 Tailwind CSS 编写一个名为 "New Arrivals" 的首页 Section
    
    1. 全局样式变量 (需易于调整)：
    
    使用 CSS 变量定义：--main-radius (圆角), --brand-red (价格/Sale色), --font-base (无衬线字体)。
    
    2. 顶部导航 (Header)：
    
    左侧：大标题 "New Arrivals" + 灰色小字描述。
    
    
    3. 核心布局 (Main Layout)：
    
    桌面端 (Desktop)： 采用 Flex 或 Grid 布局。左侧为一个固定比例的 Banner (Shop Now 按钮居中偏下)；右侧是一个 1x4 的横向网格 或可滚动的产品列表。
    
    手机端 (Mobile)： >   - 标题和描述居左对齐。
    
    左侧 Banner 变为全宽 放在最上方。
    
    下方产品改为 2x2 网格 或 横向滑动(Overflow-x-scroll) 模式。
    
    4. 产品卡片细节 (Product Card)：
    
    图片容器： 浅灰色背景 (#F3F3F3)，产品居中，整体大圆角。
    
    文字排版： 顶部是分类小字（全大写），中间是粗体标题，底部是价格
    
    颜色选项： 底部展示两个小的色块/材质方块。
    
    , 桌面端： 实现左右结构。左边 1/5 宽度是 Banner，右边 4/5 是 4 个横向排开的产品。要求 Banner 和 4 个产品卡片高度完全一致且底部对齐在同一水平线。
    
    手机端： > 1. Banner 全宽置顶。
    2. 下方产品使用 2x2 网格 形式展示。
    3. 核心要求： 开启横向滑动功能。如果超过 4 个产品，用户可以向右滑动切换到下一组 2x2 阵列。使用 scroll-snap 确保滑动停顿在网格边缘。
    
    样式控制： 使用 CSS 变量定义圆角（--radius）、主色（--primary）和字体。所有图片需带有浅灰色圆角底框，并还原图片中 Sale 标签和底部切换箭头的 UI。
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    --radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    --primary: {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    --font-base: {{ block.settings.font_family.family }}, sans-serif;
    
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    font-family: var(--font-base);
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-main-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 20%;
    position: relative;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.banner_bg_color }};
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #F3F3F3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    max-height: 200px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg_color }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-products-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-products-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_bg_color }};
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: visible;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: #F3F3F3;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 12px 12px 16px 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px;
    left: 8px;
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) / 2);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #F3F3F3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 16px 16px 16px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-category-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: {{ block.settings.category_color }};
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.product_title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-product-colors-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) / 3);
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .ai-new-arrivals-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .ai-new-arrivals-main-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 1;
      min-height: 250px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-products-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-products-scroll-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      gap: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-products-scroll-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 100%;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-products-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.nav_button_bg }};
      border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.nav_button_border }};
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
      opacity: 0.3;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:not(:disabled):hover {
      background-color: {{ block.settings.nav_button_hover_bg }};
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      stroke: {{ block.settings.nav_button_color }};
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.nav_dot_color }};
      opacity: 0.3;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-nav-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .ai-new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding | times: 0.7 }}px 16px;
    }

    .ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 12px 12px 12px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-new-arrivals-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
      {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
        <p class="ai-new-arrivals-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-main-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.banner_image %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.banner_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.banner_image.alt | escape }}"
            class="ai-new-arrivals-banner-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.banner_image.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.banner_image.height }}"
          >
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-new-arrivals-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ 'lifestyle-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        {% if block.settings.banner_button_text != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.banner_button_link }}" class="ai-new-arrivals-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.banner_button_text }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-products-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-products-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.product_list != blank %}
            {% for product in block.settings.product_list %}
              <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.sale_badge_text }}</div>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if product.featured_image %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                      alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                      class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      loading="lazy"
                      width="400"
                      height="400"
                    >
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if product.type != blank %}
                    <p class="ai-new-arrivals-product-category-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.type }}</p>
                  {% endif %}
                  
                  <h3 class="ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h3>
                  
                  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ product.price | money }}
                  </div>

                  {% if block.settings.show_color_swatches and product.options_with_values.size > 0 %}
                    {% for option in product.options_with_values %}
                      {% if option.name == 'Color' or option.name == 'Colour' %}
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-colors-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                          {% for value in option.values limit: 2 %}
                            <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: {{ value | handle }};"></div>
                          {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                      {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </a>
            {% endfor %}
          {% else %}
            {% for i in (1..4) %}
              <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if i == 1 %}
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.sale_badge_text }}</div>
                  {% endif %}
                  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <p class="ai-new-arrivals-product-category-{{ ai_gen_id }}">CATEGORY</p>
                  <h3 class="ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Product Title</h3>
                  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">$99.00</div>
                  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-colors-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #000000;"></div>
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #808080;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-products-scroll-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% assign products = block.settings.product_list %}
          {% if products == blank %}
            {% assign total_products = 8 %}
          {% else %}
            {% assign total_products = products.size %}
          {% endif %}
          
          {% assign pages = total_products | divided_by: 4.0 | ceil %}
          
          {% for page in (1..pages) %}
            <div class="ai-new-arrivals-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% assign start_index = page | minus: 1 | times: 4 %}
              {% for i in (0..3) %}
                {% assign product_index = start_index | plus: i %}
                {% if products != blank and product_index < total_products %}
                  {% assign product = products[product_index] %}
                  <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.sale_badge_text }}</div>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if product.featured_image %}
                        <img
                          src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                          alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                          class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                          loading="lazy"
                          width="400"
                          height="400"
                        >
                      {% else %}
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                          {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                        </div>
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product.type != blank %}
                        <p class="ai-new-arrivals-product-category-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.type }}</p>
                      {% endif %}
                      <h3 class="ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h3>
                      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.price | money }}</div>
                      {% if block.settings.show_color_swatches and product.options_with_values.size > 0 %}
                        {% for option in product.options_with_values %}
                          {% if option.name == 'Color' or option.name == 'Colour' %}
                            <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-colors-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                              {% for value in option.values limit: 2 %}
                                <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: {{ value | handle }};"></div>
                              {% endfor %}
                            </div>
                          {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  </a>
                {% elsif products == blank and product_index < 8 %}
                  <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product_index == 0 %}
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.sale_badge_text }}</div>
                      {% endif %}
                      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      <p class="ai-new-arrivals-product-category-{{ ai_gen_id }}">CATEGORY</p>
                      <h3 class="ai-new-arrivals-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Product Title</h3>
                      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">$99.00</div>
                      <div class="ai-new-arrivals-product-colors-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #000000;"></div>
                        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="background-color: #808080;"></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-new-arrivals-nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <button class="ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-new-arrivals-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Previous">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 19.5L8.25 12l7.5-7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-new-arrivals-nav-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
          <button class="ai-new-arrivals-nav-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-new-arrivals-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Next">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class NewArrivals{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.currentPage = 0;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.initColorSwatches();
        this.initMobileCarousel();
      }

      initColorSwatches() {
        const swatches = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-new-arrivals-color-swatch-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        swatches.forEach(swatch => {
          const bgColor = swatch.style.backgroundColor;
          if (!bgColor || bgColor === 'transparent' || bgColor === 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)') {
            swatch.style.backgroundColor = '#cccccc';
          }
        });
      }

      initMobileCarousel() {
        const scrollContainer = this.querySelector('.ai-new-arrivals-products-scroll-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const grids = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-new-arrivals-products-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const prevButton = this.querySelector('.ai-new-arrivals-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const nextButton = this.querySelector('.ai-new-arrivals-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const dotsContainer = this.querySelector('.ai-new-arrivals-nav-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

        if (!scrollContainer || grids.length === 0) return;

        const totalPages = grids.length;

        for (let i = 0; i < totalPages; i++) {
          const dot = document.createElement('div');
          dot.className = 'ai-new-arrivals-nav-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}';
          if (i === 0) dot.classList.add('active');
          dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
        }

        const dots = dotsContainer.querySelectorAll('.ai-new-arrivals-nav-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

        const updateButtons = () => {
          prevButton.disabled = this.currentPage === 0;
          nextButton.disabled = this.currentPage === totalPages - 1;
          
          dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
            if (index === this.currentPage) {
              dot.classList.add('active');
            } else {
              dot.classList.remove('active');
            }
          });
        };

        const scrollToPage = (pageIndex) => {
          const targetGrid = grids[pageIndex];
          if (targetGrid) {
            targetGrid.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest', inline: 'start' });
            this.currentPage = pageIndex;
            updateButtons();
          }
        };

        prevButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
          if (this.currentPage > 0) {
            scrollToPage(this.currentPage - 1);
          }
        });

        nextButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
          if (this.currentPage < totalPages - 1) {
            scrollToPage(this.currentPage + 1);
          }
        });

        scrollContainer.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
          const scrollLeft = scrollContainer.scrollLeft;
          const gridWidth = grids[0].offsetWidth + 16;
          const newPage = Math.round(scrollLeft / gridWidth);
          
          if (newPage !== this.currentPage) {
            this.currentPage = newPage;
            updateButtons();
          }
        });

        updateButtons();
      }
    }

    customElements.define('new-arrivals-{{ ai_gen_id }}', NewArrivals{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

